query: WITH entities AS (SELECT email, id FROM core_customers WHERE (COALESCE((email, id) < ($3, $2), $2 IS NULL)) ORDER BY email DESC, id DESC LIMIT $1) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: Repo__Id", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN core_customer_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.email desc, i.id desc, i.id, e.sequence
